seagull
Homonym Number: 3
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:a loose forward who positions himself around scrums, line-outs, rucks etc.; a forward who preferring to play very loose, away from the pack; a loose forward or breakaway scavenging for pickings on the outskirts of tight play
Origin:
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
See:
Pronunciation:
Notes: ca1950's (F. McKay, St.Patrick's College, Wellington)
