Quote:  Probably because he was a loose forward himself and appreciated the need for a `seagull', he chose me for the North Island team four years in a row, from 1953 to 1956. This was the warning given to the New Zealand fifteen forwards prior to their Rugby match with the Maoris last week at Auckland.
